oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Scenic view of Cumberland River showing Cunningham Bridge
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: "Cumberland River approaching Cunningham Bridge and Clarksville, Tenn." Color tinted photograph of the Cumberland River and a road running parallel on left. The Cunningham Bridge is visible in the distance. Features a white border and divided back. Postcard printed on linen. [No. 2B-H1284]
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: Rivers; Roads; Bridges
